    "Hey et al. [56] proposed an automated requirements classification technique called NoRBERT, which uses the transfer learning capabilities of BERT.",
    "Luo et al. [57] proposed a new requirements classification technique named PRCBERT, which is based on BERT's pre-trained language model and applies flexible prompt templates to achieve accurate classification."
